zot - minimal screenshot utility
================================

zot is a minimal screenshot utility that captures your screen and
saves it as PNG. It does one thing and does it well.


Requirements
------------
- Zig 0.15
- X11
- libpng


Installation
------------
Enter the following command to build and install zot
(if necessary as root):

    make clean install


Running zot
-----------
Simply invoke the 'zot' command:

    zot

This will capture your entire screen and save it to zot.png.


Options
-------
    -o <file>     output file (default: zot.png)
    -q <0-9>      compression quality (default: 9)

Examples:

    zot -o screenshot.png
    zot -q 5
    zot -o ~/Pictures/screen.png -q 9
